<body>
  <%- include("components/header",{username:username}) %>
  <main>
    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Todo List - Stay Organized and Productive</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to the Todo List web application, designed to help you stay organized and boost your productivity. With this simple yet powerful tool, managing your tasks and to-dos has never been easier.
      </p>
      <h3>Key Features:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Add Todo:</strong> Easily add new tasks to your list. Simply type in the task and press the "Add" button to include it in your list of todos.</li>
        <li><strong>Edit Todo:</strong> Need to make changes to an existing task? No problem! Click on the todo you wish to modify, and a user-friendly interface will allow you to update its details effortlessly.</li>
        <li><strong>Delete Todo:</strong> Completed a task or no longer need it on your list? You can quickly remove any todo by clicking on the delete button associated with it.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Our goal is to provide you with a clean and intuitive Todo List application that enhances your task management experience. Whether you are a student, professional, or simply want to stay organized in your daily life, this app is for you!
      </p>
      <p>
        So, what are you waiting for? Start organizing your tasks and stay on top of your to-dos with the Todo List application today!
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
